    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't looking for a showroom finish. The engine and transmission are solid and the car drives well, though you should expect some typical wear and tear consistent with its age. The exterior has a few minor dings and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows some staining on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It has been recently serviced, but it will likely need new tires and a brake pad replacement within the next few months. Overall, it's a functional, honest car that gets the job done at an affordable price point.",
