      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner! While it currently requires significant mechanical work and shows considerable wear inside and out, it offers a solid foundation for someone with the right tools and vision. It's priced to sell and waiting for the right person to bring it back to its full potential!",
