    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it runs smoothly and looks great too! It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and style, just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
